name: Labyrinth (itch) (TransGame668)
description:
Contains 15 Level. In this game to collect 10 cubes for win, Don't hit the X sign like an hole or the ball would respawn to the original position. Every 5 level the cubes is different example: Fruit (1-5), Vegetables (6-10) and Gold (11-15).

Controls: WASD for Move.
